+<p>Every trip uses a 'bathtub' — a large box with games, materials and cleaning supplies. Order yours directly below: fill out the form and your order is sent as a nicely formatted email to <a href="mailto:sbukabs@pf.dk">sbukabs@pf.dk</a>. You'll automatically receive a copy as confirmation.</p>
+
+<p>Please use the comments field if you need help picking up the bathtub. Otherwise we assume your own KABS will help with pick-up and drop-off.</p>
+
+<p>If you run into trouble with the bathtub or have questions about your order, contact your nearest KABS or email <a href="mailto:sbukabs@pf.dk">sbukabs@pf.dk</a>.</p>
+
+<p><b>Make sure to place your order at least two weeks before the bathtub is needed, so we have time to pack it.</b></p>
+
